title: Grande Prairie Roman Catholic Separate School District No. 28
text:
Grande Prairie Roman Catholic Separate School District No. 28 or Grande Prairie and District Catholic Schools is a <a href="separate%20school">separate school</a> <a href="School%20authority">authority</a> within the Canadian province of <a href="Alberta">Alberta</a> operated out of <a href="Grande%20Prairie">Grande Prairie</a>.
